Jiaro Mendez and Elias Acevedo got into fight on April 14 just before 1am . 
 Police said the men were taken to hospital with lacerations on their bodies . 
 The pair were found to be 'highly intoxicated' as officers arrived at scene . 
 Mendez said Acevedo hit him in the head with beer bottle and stole his car . 
 Acevedo, 21, was arrested and charged with assault with a deadly weapon . 
 